<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 12:38:24 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>心力衰竭的基因治疗：对线粒体功能障碍的影响</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/gene-therapy-for-heart-failure-impact-on-mitochondrial-dysfunction</link><description>线粒体是维持心脏功能的重要组成部分，针对线粒体可能是治疗心力衰竭（HF）的一种有前途的方法。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/gene-therapy-for-heart-failure-impact-on-mitochondrial-dysfunction.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 12:38:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/gene-therapy-for-heart-failure-impact-on-mitochondrial-dysfunction</guid></item><item><title>三星为 GDC 带来裸眼 3D 游戏和 HDR10+</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/samsung-brings-glasses-free-3d-gaming-and-hdr10-to-gdc</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 12:23:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/samsung-brings-glasses-free-3d-gaming-and-hdr10-to-gdc</guid></item><item><title>物理学家终于在实验室中实现了长期预测的二维拓扑晶体</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/physicists-finally-realize-long-predicted-2d-topological-crystal-in-the-lab</link><description>芬兰的研究人员通过实验实现了人们长期预测的一类量子材料：二维拓扑晶体绝缘体。于韦斯屈莱大学和阿尔托大学（芬兰）的物理学家成功创建了二维拓扑晶体绝缘体&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/physicists-finally-realize-long-predicted-2d-topological-crystal-in-the-lab.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 12:08:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/physicists-finally-realize-long-predicted-2d-topological-crystal-in-the-lab</guid></item><item><title>有史以来最大规模的射电天空勘测以前所未有的细节绘制了宇宙图</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/largest-ever-radio-sky-survey-maps-the-universe-in-unprecedented-detail</link><description>使用低频阵列 (LOFAR) 的国际合作发布了极其详细的射电天空图，揭示了 1370 万个宇宙源，并提供了迄今为止最完整的活跃增长的超大质量黑洞普查。它展示了由这些黑洞提供动力的各种不同寻常的系统，其无线电发射可以延伸到数百万光年。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/largest-ever-radio-sky-survey-maps-the-universe-in-unprecedented-detail.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 11:53:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/largest-ever-radio-sky-survey-maps-the-universe-in-unprecedented-detail</guid></item><item><title>通用疫苗即将问世：鼻喷雾剂可保护小鼠免受呼吸道病毒、细菌和过敏原的侵害</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/closing-in-on-a-universal-vaccine-nasal-spray-protects-mice-from-respiratory-viruses-bacteria-and-allergens</link><description>在医学进步领域，一种可以预防任何病原体的通用疫苗长期以来一直是一个圣杯，而且就像神话中的容器一样难以捉摸。但斯坦福大学医学院的研究人员和合作者在这一探索中迈出了惊人的一步，甚至连他们自己都感到惊讶。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/closing-in-on-a-universal-vaccine-nasal-spray-protects-mice-from-respiratory-viruses-bacteria-and-allergens.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 11:38:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/closing-in-on-a-universal-vaccine-nasal-spray-protects-mice-from-respiratory-viruses-bacteria-and-allergens</guid></item><item><title>带状疱疹疫苗可以延缓衰老吗？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/can-the-shingles-vaccine-slow-ageing</link><description>新研究指出带状疱疹疫苗可有效减少晚年患痴呆症或轻度认知能力下降的人数&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/can-the-shingles-vaccine-slow-ageing.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 11:23:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/can-the-shingles-vaccine-slow-ageing</guid></item><item><title>免疫的宏观生态学：气候对无脊椎动物免疫反应的主要影响</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-macroecology-of-immunity-predominant-influence-of-climate-on-invertebrate-immune-response</link><description>https://vist.ly/4u8bp &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-macroecology-of-immunity-predominant-influence-of-climate-on-invertebrate-immune-response2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 11:08:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-macroecology-of-immunity-predominant-influence-of-climate-on-invertebrate-immune-response</guid></item><item><title>PSMA-PET 和 MR 引导局部增强前列腺 SBRT 后的 PSA 和 PSMA 动力学：II 期 PROBE 试验的结果</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/psa-and-psma-kinetics-after-psma-pet-mr-guided-prostate-sbrt-with-focal-boost-results-from-the-phase-ii-probe-trial</link><description>PSMA 引导的局部增强前列腺 SBRT 后的 PSA 和 PSMA 动力学。标记和吸收动力学可以告诉我们好、坏和丑陋吗？在 RedJournal 上阅读相关内容&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/psa-and-psma-kinetics-after-psma-pet-mr-guided-prostate-sbrt-with-focal-boost-results-from-the-phase-ii-probe-trial2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 10:53:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/psa-and-psma-kinetics-after-psma-pet-mr-guided-prostate-sbrt-with-focal-boost-results-from-the-phase-ii-probe-trial</guid></item><item><title>运动可以预防阿尔茨海默氏症，科学家们终于知道原因了</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/exercise-protects-against-alzheimers-and-scientists-may-finally-know-why</link><description>在其众多的健康益处中，身体活动&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/exercise-protects-against-alzheimers-and-scientists-may-finally-know-why.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 10:38:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/exercise-protects-against-alzheimers-and-scientists-may-finally-know-why</guid></item><item><title>哈伯德激子的量子控制</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/quantum-control-of-hubbard-excitons</link><description>Floquet 工程正在成为一种控制量子材料的工具。在这里，它使用非共振光场来相干地修饰 Sr2CuO3 中的哈伯德激子，驱动亮态和暗态之间的波函数旋转。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/quantum-control-of-hubbard-excitons.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 10:23:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/quantum-control-of-hubbard-excitons</guid></item></channel></rss>